Writable datasets refer to datasets that have an access level of 'write'; 
Anomalies are a type of dataset; 
Latest version refers to the version with the highest version number; 
Average feature value is the average value of the features in a dataset.

; 
; For the purpose of this query, a "major change" is assumed to be any change in the version that includes the string 'major' in its description, indicating a significant update or alteration.
; 
; The "average version creation year" is calculated based on the version creation dates that fall within the year 2023, providing insight into the dataset's update frequency within that specific year.
